<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Shouren's blog - Shouren</title><link href="http://blog.shouren.me/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="http://blog.shouren.me/feeds/shouren.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>http://blog.shouren.me/</id><updated>2017-01-23T16:20:00+08:00</updated><entry><title>Note for Let's Encrypt</title><link href="http://blog.shouren.me/note-for-let's-encrypt.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2017-01-23T16:20:00+08:00</published><updated>2017-01-23T16:20:00+08:00</updated><author><name>Shouren</name></author><id>tag:blog.shouren.me,2017-01-23:/note-for-let's-encrypt.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Note for ssl cert&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h3&gt;Installing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For CentOS 7&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo yum install cerbot
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Geting Cert&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;webroot: For website which is running&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;standalone: Opposite of above&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;cerbot certonly
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Renewing Cert&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Testing renew first&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;certbot renew --dry-run
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do renew cert&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;certbot renew --quiet
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><category term="HTTPs"></category></entry></feed>